Ganyu Impact Mobile(Genshin Impact Fan Game) is an adventure game developed by DjalalxJay. It came out on 16-09-2022.
Ganyu Impact Mobile(Genshin Impact Fan Game) is available on Android. The game is sold via itch.io.
